{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/k8s_prac_10/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p><em>해당 포스트는 교재 『쿠버네티스 교과서』를 활용하며,</em><br>\n<em>환경은 Kubernetes v1.28. Docker Desktop으로 진행합니다.</em></p>\n<h2 id=\"개념-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"개념 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개념 요약</h2>\n<h3 id=\"helm-헬름\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#helm-%ED%97%AC%EB%A6%84\" aria-label=\"helm 헬름 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Helm 헬름</h3>\n<p>여러개의 YAML 정의 스크립트를 하나의 아티팩트로 묶어 리포지토리에 공유할 수 있다. 헬름 명령으로 컨피그맵, 디플로이먼트, 서비스등의 애플리케이션을 설치할 수 있다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>애플리케이션 수준의 추상화를 도와준다</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"헬름-리포지터리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%97%AC%EB%A6%84-%EB%A6%AC%ED%8F%AC%EC%A7%80%ED%84%B0%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"헬름 리포지터리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>헬름 리포지터리</h3>\n<p>서버에서 사용 가능한 모든 패키지의 색인을 제공, 로컬에 저장했다가 패키지 검색에 사용.</p>\n<h3 id=\"차트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%A8%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"차트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>차트</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>애플리케이션의 패키지.</li>\n<li>로컬 컴퓨터에서 만들거나 리포지터리에 배포 가능.</li>\n<li>릴리스 이름을 달리해가며 하나의 클러스터에 같은 차트를 여러 개 설치가능.</li>\n<li>YAML 매니페스트를 포함한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"release-객체\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#release-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4\" aria-label=\"release 객체 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Release 객체</h3>\n<p>install 또는 upgrade 명령을 실행할 때 관련 정보를 담아 생성되는 객체.</p>\n<h3 id=\"values-객체\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#values-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4\" aria-label=\"values 객체 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Values 객체</h3>\n<p>차트에 포함된 기본 값에 사용자가 지정한 값을 오버라이드한 정보를 담아 생성되는 객체.</p>\n<h3 id=\"helm-차트-파일-구조\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#helm-%EC%B0%A8%ED%8A%B8-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0\" aria-label=\"helm 차트 파일 구조 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Helm 차트 파일 구조</h3>\n<p>필요한 3가지 요소</p>\n<ol>\n<li>chart.yaml<br>\n차트의 메타데이터를 저장</li>\n<li>values.yaml<br>\n파라미터의 기본 값을 기록</li>\n<li>templates 디렉터리<br>\n템플릿 변수가 포함된 매니페스트 파일을 담은 디렉터리</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"helm-리포지터리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#helm-%EB%A6%AC%ED%8F%AC%EC%A7%80%ED%84%B0%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"helm 리포지터리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Helm 리포지터리</h3>\n<p>웹 서버에 저장된 차트와 버전의 목록이 담긴 인덱스!</p>\n<ol>\n<li>공식 헬름 리포지터리(도커 허브와 유사한 느낌)</li>\n<li>차트뮤지엄으로 만든 리포지터리(로컬에서 직접 설정가능)</li>\n<li>기타 다른 웹 서버의 리포지터리</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"실습\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8B%A4%EC%8A%B5\" aria-label=\"실습 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>실습</h2>\n<h3 id=\"주요-요점들\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94-%EC%9A%94%EC%A0%90%EB%93%A4\" aria-label=\"주요 요점들 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>주요 요점들</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Helm 템플릿으로 조건문이나 반복문 설정도 가능하다</li>\n<li>Helm은 하나의 차트로 동일한 애플리케이션을 여러개 실행할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"매니페스트-파일\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%A4%EB%8B%88%ED%8E%98%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"매니페스트 파일 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>매니페스트 파일</h3>\n<p>web-ping-deployment.yaml</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">apiVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> apps/v1\r\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">kind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Deployment\r\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">metadata</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> .Release.Name <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">labels</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">kiamol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> .Values.kiamolChapter <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">spec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">selector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">matchLabels</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">app</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> web<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>ping\r\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">instance</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> .Release.Name <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">metadata</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">labels</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">app</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> web<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>ping\r\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">instance</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> .Release.Name <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">spec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">containers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> app\r\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> kiamol/ch10<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>web<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>ping\r\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> TARGET\r\n              <span class=\"token key atrule\">value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuat